description: This file is the entry point for a React-based frontend application. It imports React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the main App component. It initializes the React application by creating a root and rendering the App component inside React.StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root to render a React component tree into a DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the DOM at the specified root.
